[root@DEV-SERVER ~]# 

need to update password authentication

for this there will be a specific path is

vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config

in this file go to line no:65

put like this below

PasswordAuthentication yes

again  go to line no:40 

here do remove # hashtag and made changes like below

PermitRootLogin yes

now do restart sshd

systemctl restart sshd--------------------> command to restart sshd

